  <content contentuid="hf1e86a9701da4d25b6fefe0080cfdbace14d" version="1">Scribing a scroll requires a full uninterrupted day to make progress.&lt;br&gt;Engaging in combat or taking a short rest outside of camp will pause scribing for the day.</content>
  <content contentuid="h6c66bf5bad3748bc98951e591759a2018ebc" version="1">Engaging in combat or taking a short rest outside of camp will progress scribing by 2 hours as light activity during long rest.&lt;br&gt;Staying in camp for a day will progress scribing by full 8 hours.</content>
  <content contentuid="hcc5f8361516249fb8b2c51375b5bd418d66g" version="1">Each long rest counts as 1 day of scribing without any additional conditions.</content>
